text: Aman Saini is an Indian Archer. He won the Silver Medal Asian Games 2018 in the Men's compound archery team event. He completed his studies at Richmond's global school, Delhi, and trained under his coach Surender Garg. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Indian archers Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games silver medalists for India Category:Asian Games medalists in archery Category:Archers at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
